Ordered several of these for my son.  He got them exactly when the tracking number said it would arrive and he enjoys them very much.

These seasons contain the uncut, and remastered episodes of Dragonball Z's Android and Cell Sagas. The episodes are remastered in 1080p and they give you a variety of choices on how you want to watch it. You can watch the episodes with the original Japanese soundtracks, or the North American soundtracks. You also have the choice of watching it in Japanese dialogue with or without subtitles. Great buy for any Dragonball fan!
The product was exactly as described and showed up quick. Would purchase from again. Thanks for everything. Go Dragonball Z!
